<item>
            <title>[LU-2072] Leak of s_mb_prealloc_table in ldiskfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2072</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;All 2.x versions at least seems to be affected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems ext4-prealloc-rhel6.patch adds sbi-&amp;gt;s_mb_prealloc_table field that is allocated using kmalloc (128 bytes on my system) and is never freed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Needs to be freed in ldiskfs_mb_release&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="16212">LU-2072</key>
